data.description: Embrace the opportunity to make this well-located home in "The Farm," Wildomar, your own masterpiece. This 5 bedroom, 3 bath home offers tremendous potential with its desirable features. While it may need a little TLC, the solid foundation and layout are here to work with. The main level showcases a bedroom, an open kitchen with granite countertops, a dining room, and a three-car garage. Upstairs, a spacious bonus room with double doors was converted to the 5th bedroom. The main bedroom retreat is a standout, boasting a private balcony, an expansive walk-in closet, a vanity area, and an ensuite/sitting room. There are two additional bedrooms that are generous in size down the hall from the main bedroom. With solar power and no rear neighbors, the setting is ideal. Explore the possibilities to transform this property into your dream home—all at an appealing price point. Don't miss this chance to add your personal touch and create a haven that reflects your unique style and vision.
